msgid "gluon-config-mode:welcome"
msgstr ""
"Welcome the the setup wizard of your new Freifunk Saar node. "
"Please fill out the following form and transmit it."

msgid "gluon-config-mode:pubkey"
msgstr ""
"<!-- empty -->"

msgid "gluon-config-mode:reboot"
msgstr ""
"<p>"
"The node is currently rebooting and will try to connect to other "
"nearby Freifunk Saar nodes after that. "
"You can find lots of information on the Freifunk Saar community on "
"<a href=\"https://saar.freifunk.net/\">our homepage</a>. "
"</p><p>"
"Please register on the <a href=\"https://lists.hacksaar.de/listinfo/freifunk-announcements\">announcement list</a> so that we can contact you for important news."
"</p><p>"
"Next, you could... "
"<ul>"
"<li>... <a href=\"https://lists.hacksaar.de/listinfo/freifunk-public\">join our public discussion list</a>.</li>"
"<li>... give the <a href=\"mailto:freifunk-vpn@saar.freifunk.net\">admin team</a> some feedback.</li>"
"<li>... go <a href=\"https://www.hacksaar.de/anfahrt/\">fetch some stickers</a>.</li>"
"<li>... <a href=\"https://www.twitter.com/FreifunkSaar\">follow Freifunk Saar on Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FreifunkSaar\">like us on Facebook</a> or subscribe to our <a href=\"https://saar.freifunk.net/feed/\">RSS feed</a> to get all the important news about Freifunk.</li>"
"<li>... or spread the idea: Help your neighbor to set up a Freifunk node. Do the same on the other side of the street!</li>"
"</ul>"
"</p><p>"
"To get back to this configuration interface, press the reset button for "
"10 seconds during normal operation. The device will then reboot into config "
"mode. The LEDs will be blinking. It takes about 60 seconds until the configuration "
"is available at <a href=\"http://192.168.1.1\">http://192.168.1.1</a>. "
"</p><p>"
"Enjoy your Freifunk node and have fun exploring the Freifunk network! "
"</p>"
